overview: Tasha (Romi Rain) is a happily married woman who loves her ordinary sex toys. Yet, she yearns for something extraordinary. She wants the most powerful, versatile, ride-on-top vibrator in the world, with attachments that buzz, twirl, and go all the way to "11"... The Motorbunny. To pay for her pricey acquisition, Tasha devises a plan to make her Motorbunny available to her closest girlfriends by launching a Sex Machine Club. Hop on!
title: The Motorbunny Club 1
